ing","points":55},{"label":"gravitational lens modelling","points":28}],"must_read_reason":"strong gravitational lensing","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing","Galaxy Evolution"]},{"id":"2606.19454","canonical_id":"2606.19454","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Baryonic mass budgets in the central regions of the Bullet Cluster and their consistency with strong lensing in MOND","authors":["Dong Zhang","Hosein Haghi","Elena Asencio","Indranil Banik","Akram Hasani Zonoozi","Sangjun Cha","Boseong Young Cho","Hyungjin Joo","Pavel Kroupa","Anastasia Lazutkina","Eda Gjergo"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA","astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"子弹头星团的强引力透镜观测传统上被视为暗物质的强证据和对MOND理论的挑战。本文利用IGIMF理论重新估计了星团核心区的重子质量，发现MOND强透镜质量落在IGIMF模型预测范围内，表明在IGIMF框架下重子质量预算与MOND要求一致，但剩余物质的空间分布和动力学行为仍需验证。","date":"2026-06-19","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.19454","score":92,"stars":5,"tier":"must-read","mandatory":true,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"strong gravitational lensing","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2606.19428","canonical_id":"2606.19428","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Cooling, conduction, compact objects: Gravothermal evolution of dissipative self-interacting dark matter halos","authors":["Ludwig D. Schmidt","Moritz S. Fischer","Mathias Garny"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO","astro-ph.GA","hep-ph"],"summary":"本文系统研究了耗散性自相互作用暗物质对孤立暗物质晕引力热演化的影响，发现耗散能显著改变演化过程，并可能解释近期观测到的强透镜扰动体特征。","date":"2026-06-19","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.19428","score":99,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2606.21361","canonical_id":"2606.21361","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Extended [CII] gas emission in and around a massive quiescent galaxy at z=7.3","authors":["F. Valentino","A. Pensabene","A. Weibel","A. de Graaff","D. J. Setton","P. Oesch","G. Brammer","W. M. Baker","R. Bezanson","J. E. Greene","K. E. Heintz","K. Ito","M. Lee","J. Leja","J. Matthee","B. Wang","K. E. Whitaker","C. C. Williams","P. Zhu"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"在红移z=7.27的遥远静止星系RUBIES-UDS-QG-z7中发现[CII] 158微米发射线，其延伸至8千秒差距的晕状结构，远超致密的恒星主体（209秒差距）。该星系虽保有大量冷气体（气体分数>20%），但恒星形成效率极低，暗示存在高效的恒星形成抑制机制。","date":"2026-06-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.21361","score":95,"stars":5,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"galaxy gas","points":10}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Multi-phase and Molecular Gas","Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2606.23683","canonical_id":"2606.23683","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Little Red Dots on FIRE: Exploring the formation and observational signatures of ultra-compact early galaxies","authors":["Niranjan Chandra Roy","Daniel Anglés-Alcázar","Rachel K. Cochrane","Alexander J. Richings","Jonathan Mercedes-Feliz","Christopher C. Hayward","Claude-André Faucher-Giguère","Erini Lambrides","Robert Feldmann","Boon Kiat Oh","Andrew Marszewski","Guochao Sun","Kelcey Davis","Jed McKinney","Caitlin M. Casey","Tanio Díaz-Santos","Madisyn Brooks","Grace Farrell"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文利用FIRE宇宙学模拟和3D尘埃辐射传输，研究了“小红点”（LRDs）的起源。发现早期宇宙中极端致密的恒星核（半径<300 pc）可以在不依赖活动星系核（AGN）的情况下再现部分LRD观测特征（如巴尔默跳变、UV光谱斜率等），但无法解释红色光学连续谱和更极端的谱线宽度，因此提出恒星+AGN混合模型：致密恒星核负责UV和中等宽度谱线，AGN贡献红色连续谱和极端谱线。","date":"2026-06-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.23683","score":91,"stars":5,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2606.21614","canonical_id":"2606.21614","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Little Red and Blue Dots: AGN-excited narrow lines, Lyman-$α$ emission, and resemblance to standard quasars","authors":["Sophia Geris","Roberto Maiolino","Xihan Ji","Guido Risaliti","Giorgio Lanzuisi","Francesco D'Eugenio","Yuki Isobe","Gareth Jones","Anishya Harshan","Matilde Brazzini","Ignas Juodžbalis","Jan Scholtz","Pierluigi Rinaldi","Hannah Übler","William Baker","Andrew J. Bunker","Marcella Brusa","Stefano Carniani","Stephane Charlot","Mirko Curti","Andrea Comastri","Emma Curtis Lake","Roberto Gilli","Kevin Hainline","Piero Madau","Stefano Marchesi","Giovanni Mazzolari","Lorenzo Napolitano","Eleonora Parlanti","Laura Pentericci","Cristina Ramos Almeida","Brant Robertson","Maddie S. Silcock","Roberta Tripodi","Giacomo Venturi","Cristian Vignali","Fabio Vito","Yongda Zhu"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA","astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"本文分析了36个小红点和蓝点（LRDs和LBDs）的JWST样本，发现它们都由黑洞驱动，具有宽巴尔默线但极弱的X射线辐射。研究指出LRD的完全包裹黑洞的气体包层模型与观测不符，需引入团块性或赤道几何结构。LRD可能是尘埃遮蔽的LBD，且其各向同性辐射假设下的光度估计不准确。","date":"2026-06-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.21614","score":88,"stars":5,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2606.20801","canonical_id":"2606.20801","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"LEGGOS III: Mapping Star Formation and Dust in Gravitationally Lensed Galaxies with $\\textit{SUMAC}$, a UMAP and Clustering Framework","authors":["Alex Ross","Gourav Khullar","Taylor Hutchison","Dylan Berry","Aritra Ghosh","T. Emil Rivera-Thorsen","Guillaume Mahler","Brian Welch","Pedram Abedi","Cole Panzer","Michael Florian","Julissa Sarmiento","the JWST LEGGOS Collaboration"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA","astro-ph.IM"],"summary":"SUMAC是一个基于UMAP和HDBSCAN的无监督学习管道，能够在单像素级别自动分割JWST成像与光谱数据，识别透镜星系中的星族区域，并在SGAS111020.0+645950.8星系中成功恢复出六个物理上不同的恒星/星云群体。","date":"2026-06-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.20801","score":88,"stars":5,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2606.19995","canonical_id":"2606.19995","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Finite-Core Signatures in LISA-Band Wave-Optics Lensing by Low-Mass Dark Matter Halos","authors":["Dejiang Li","Tonghua Liu","Kai Liao","Beining Xia","Cuihong Wen","Jieci Wang"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO","gr-qc"],"summary":"本文研究了LISA频段引力波被暗物质晕衍射透镜效应，发现有限核结构会在波光学放大因子中留下独特特征，可用于探测暗物质晕的内部密度分布。","date":"2026-06-19","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.19995","score":88,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2606.20809","canonical_id":"2606.20809","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"The Lifecycle and Emission Properties of PAHs in Cosmological Hydrodynamic Galaxy Formation Simulations","authors":["Desika Narayanan","Paul Torrey","Massimiliano Parente","Grant Donnelly","Dhruv Zimmerman","Alex Garcia","Helena Richie","J. -D. T. Smith","Brandon Hensley","Federico Marinacci","Jed McKinney","Alexandra Pope","Gergo Popping","Laura Sales","Karin Sandstrom","Ethan Savitch","Irene Shivaei","Justin Spilker","Corey Whitcomb"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文构建了首个从z=6到z=0的星系演化中多环芳烃（PAHs）生命周期与光度的宇宙学模型，提出星际介质中尘埃-尘埃碎裂是PAHs形成的主要机制，成功再现了PAH质量分数演化、PAH-金属丰度关系等关键观测特征。","date":"2026-06-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.20809","score":85,"stars":4,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"galaxy gas","points":10}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Multi-phase and Molecular Gas","Dust and ISM","Galaxy Evolution"]}],"must_read":[{"id":"2606.21519","canonical_id":"2606.21519","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Wave-optics imprints of dark matter subhalos on strongly lensed gravitational waves. II. Saddle images and detectability","authors":["Shin'ichiro Ando"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO","astro-ph.HE","gr-qc"],"summary":"本文研究了强引力透镜引力波中的波光学干涉效应对暗物质次结构的探测能力，提出了一种时域方法计算鞍点像的放大因子，并评估了LISA探测器的检测能力。结果表明，在冷暗物质次结构模型下，LISA有望在任务期内探测到10-20个次结构事件，为10⁴-10⁷ M⊙尺度上的暗物质次结构提供新的探测手段。","date":"2026-06-23","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.21519","score":100,"stars":5,"tier":"must-read","mandatory":true,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"stron